These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, sudoku, chess
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Hobby   | sudoku     | card-games    | chess   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: go, snooker, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Game   | go    | canasta        | snooker |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, canasta
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing poker is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Game   | snooker | poker     | canasta |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, family, disaster
1. the fan of funk is the person watching drama movies##1
2. the fan of soul is between the person watching family movies and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Movie-Genre           | family | disaster | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, accountant, firefighter
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the doctor is between the firefighter and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Job     | firefighter    | doctor | accountant    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
City: rome, london, new-york
1. the person traveling to rome is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person traveling to london##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| City         | london | rome | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
House: victorian, tower, cape-cod
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the brazilian is between the cape-cod house and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| House          | tower  | victorian  | cape-cod |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian | dutch     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person drinking lemonade is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | cola  | lemonade  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

