.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, family
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre         | family | sports | adventure |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

