.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, action, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is between the person drinking fanta and the person watching superhero movies##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Movie-Genre       | action  | horror | superhero |

