.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
3 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, goat
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Pet         | chinchilla | goat | dog |

