1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the motorbike and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Hobby         | collecting | puzzles  | skydiving       |
| Transport   | subway | train | motorbike |

