.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, polish
3 different games are played: whist, backgammon, billiard
1. the person playing whist is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| Game         | billiard  | whist | backgammon |

