.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, spanish, british
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the indonesian is on the right of the spanish##1
2. the spanish is between the british and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Nationality      | british | spanish   | indonesian |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 